import React, {Suspense, lazy} from "react";
import {Redirect, Route, Switch} from "react-router-dom";
const Dashboard = lazy(() => import("../dashboard/Dashboard"));

export default function HomePage() {
    return (
        <Suspense fallback={<LayoutSplashScreen/>}>
            <Switch>
                {
                    /* Redirect from root URL to /dashboard. */
                    <Redirect exact from="/" to="/dashboard"/>
                }
                {/* Route other */}
                <Route path="/dashboard" component={Dashboard}/>
                <Route path="/Test" component={Test}/>

                {/* <Redirect to="Error403" /> */}
                <Route path="/Error403" component={Error403}/>

                {/* <Redirect to="Customer" /> */}
                <Route path="/User/List/:Type" component={ListUser}/>
                <Route path="/Users/:Type" component={ListUser}/>

                <Route path="/User/AddNew/:role" component={AddUser}/>
                <Route path="/User/Edit" component={EditUser}/>

                <Route path="/Category/:pageType" component={CategoryTopic}/>
                <Route path="/EmojiState" component={EmojiState}/>

                {/* <Redirect to="Question" /> */}
                <Route path="/Exercise/Add" component={AddNewExercise}/>
                <Route path="/Exercise/List" component={ListExercise}/>
                <Route path="/Exercise/Edit/:id" component={AddNewExercise}/>

                <Route path="/Workout/Add" component={AddWorkout}/>
                <Route path="/Workout/List" component={ListWorkout}/>
                <Route path="/Workout/Detail/:id" component={AddWorkout}/>

                <Route path="/Question/Add" component={AddQuestion}/>
                <Route path="/Question/Update/:id" component={AddQuestion}/>
                <Route path="/Question/List" component={ListQuestion}/>

                <Route path="/Dialog/Add" component={AddDialog}/>
                <Route path="/Dialog/Update/:id" component={AddDialog}/>
                <Route path="/Dialog/List" component={ListDialog}/>

                <Route path="/Field/Add/:businessId" component={AddField}/>
                <Route path="/Field/Update/:businessId/:id" component={AddField}/>
                <Route path="/Field/List" component={ListField}/>

                <Route path="/Form/Add/:businessId" component={AddForm}/>
                <Route path="/Form/Update/:businessId/:id" component={AddForm}/>
                <Route path="/Form/List" component={ListForm}/>

                <Route path="/Emoji/Add" component={AddEmoji}/>
                <Route path="/Emoji/Add-Business/:businessId" component={AddEmoji}/>
                <Route path="/Emoji/Update/:id" component={AddEmoji}/>
                <Route path="/Emoji/Update-Business/:id/:businessId" component={AddEmoji}/>
                <Route path="/Emoji/List" component={ListEmoji}/>
                <Route path="/Emoji/EmojiType" component={EmojiType}/>

                <Route path="/Business/List" component={ListBusiness}/>
                <Route path="/Business/Add" component={AddBusiness}/>
                <Route path="/Business/Detail/:id/AccessCodeDetail/:accessId" component={AccessCodeDetail}/>

                <Route path="/Business/Detail/:id" component={DetailBusiness}/>
                <Route path="/Business/AddUserToBusiness" component={AddUserToBusiness}/>

                <Route path="/Module/Add" component={AddModule}/>
                <Route path="/Module/Update/:id" component={AddModule}/>
                <Route path="/Module/List" component={ListModule}/>

                <Route path="/SubModule/Add/:module" component={AddSubModule}/>
                <Route path="/SubModule/Update/:module/:id" component={AddSubModule}/>
                <Route path="/SubModule/List/:module" component={ListSubModule}/>


            </Switch>
        </Suspense>
    );
}
